    sigma_k (xi_8) = xi_8^k ==> cases(sigma_3^2 (xi_8) = sigma_3 (xi_8^3) = xi_8^9 eq.triple_(mod 8) xi_8, sigma_5^2 (xi_8) = sigma_5 (xi_8^5) = xi_8^25 eq.triple_(mod 8) xi_8, sigma_7^2 (xi_8) = sigma_7 (xi_8^7) = xi_8^49 eq.triple_(mod 8) xi_1)
